Package simulation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Simulator
    Interface class that describes a simulator
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Ant
    This is a model class to hold ant information
    AntMove
    This is a subclass of Event representing an Ant transverse between two adjacent nodes
    Evaporate
    This is a subclass of Event representing a evaporation of pheromones of an Edge.
    Observation
    This is a subclass of Event responsible for monitorizing the simulation evolution
    Run
    Run.java This is the main class.
    Simulation
    Simulation.java This is a model class that holds the information about the simulation (parameters, ant colony, pending event container, graph...)
    SimulatorAbs
    This is an abstract class that holds the generic information about a simulator implemented with a PEC (instant and PEC) and implements the interface Simulator.java
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NextMoveNotFoundException
    Exception that should be raised when the next node to go is not found in a graph.
